    <h1>Privacy Policy – Zpresto</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> December 15, 2025</p>
    <p>Zpresto (“we”, “our”, “us”) is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information when you use the Zpresto mobile application and website.</p>
    <p>By using Zpresto, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.</p>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. Account Registration and Verification</h2>
        <p>To use certain features of the Zpresto app, users may create an account. During account registration, we may collect basic personal information such as name, email address, phone number, and delivery address.</p>
        <p>We use email verification codes to verify user accounts and improve security.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect only the information necessary to provide our services:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Delivery address</li>
            <li>Location data (GPS), only when permitted by the user</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not collect unnecessary or unrelated personal data.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>3. Location Information</h2>
        <p>Zpresto may request access to your device’s GPS location to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Check service availability</li>
            <li>Assist with accurate delivery</li>
            <li>Improve address selection</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Location access is optional and can be enabled or disabled at any time through your device settings.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information only for legitimate business purposes, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Creating and managing user accounts</li>
            <li>Verifying user identity</li>
            <li>Processing and delivering orders</li>
            <li>Communicating about orders or delivery</li>
            <li>Providing customer support</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not use your data for advertising or marketing purposes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>5. Payment Information</h2>
        <p>Zpresto does not collect, store, or process any online payment information. All payments are made through Cash on Delivery (COD) at the time of order delivery.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>6. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties. Your data is not shared except when required to fulfill your order or comply with legal obligations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>7. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable and appropriate measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, misuse, loss, or alteration. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>8. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain personal data only for as long as necessary to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Provide our services</li>
            <li>Fulfill legal or operational requirements</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Users may request deletion of their data at any time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>9. Account and Data Deletion</h2>
        <p>Users can request deletion of their account or personal data by contacting us via email. Upon verification, we will delete the data unless retention is required by law.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>10. Children’s Privacy</h2>
        <p>Zpresto does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. If we become aware that such information has been collected, we will take steps to delete it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>11. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated “Last updated” date. We encourage users to review this policy periodically.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:zprestoindia@gmail.com">zprestoindia@gmail.com</a></li>
            <li>Phone: 9052750136</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
